r 18m low bake commercial vehicle spray booth the paint finish on your vehicle will be of an exceptionally high standard.</p>\n<p>On completion of repairs we can arrange our sign writer to make and apply decals to your vehicle, or if you would prefer to use your own sign writer we can liase with them to ensure your vehicle is ready for the road in its pre-accident condition.</p>\n<p>On all insurance work the final invoice for the repair will be forwarded direct to your insurance company who will pay us directly (excluding excess or VAT applicable).  This means you do not have to pay for the repairs yourself and wait for your insurance company to reimburse you.</p>\";s:10:\"field_ft_2\";s:4:\"none\";s:10:\"field_id_3\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"field_ft_3\";s:5:\"xhtml\";s:10:\"field_id_4\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"field_ft_4\";s:4:\"none\";}'), ('99', '24', '2', '2', '1224726177', 'a:22:{s:9:\"weblog_id\";s:1:\"2\";s:8:\"entry_id\";s:2:\"24\";s:9:\"author_id\";s:1:\"2\";s:10:\"new_weblog\";s:1:\"2\";s:6:\"status\";s:4:\"open\";s:10:\"entry_date\";s:19:\"2006-12-10 03:58 PM\";s:15:\"expiration_date\";s:0:\"\";s:23:\"comment_expiration_date\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"trackback_urls\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"versioning_enabled\";s:1:\"y\";s:5:\"title\";s:9:\"Vacancies\";s:9:\"url_title\";s:9:\"vacancies\";s:6:\"submit\";s:6:\"Update\";s:4:\"mode\";s:6:\"normal\";s:10:\"field_id_1\";s:183:\"Commercial Colours Ltd have been growing steadily since our relocation in August 2005. We plan to expand during years to come and would welcome a good database of potential employees.\";s:10:\"field_ft_1\";s:5:\"xhtml\";s:10:\"field_id_2\";s:529:\"<p>If you are looking for work in the Bodyshop trade and have experience in working with commercial vehicles please forward your CV to Mark Jacques at:</p>\n\n<div class=\\\"vcard\\\">\n<div class=\\\"fn org\\\">Commercial Colours</div>\n<div class=\\\"adr\\\">\n<div class=\\\"street-address\\\">Zone 3, Link 56, Weighbridge Road</div>\n<div>Deeside Industrial Park</div>\n<div