d_1\";s:247:\"Commercial Colours caters for the lighter side of accident repairs, from car derived vans such as Astravans, Berlingos, Partners, Connects right up to Ford Transits, VW Crafters and Mercedes Sprinters, evan the long wheel base high roof versions. \";s:10:\"field_ft_1\";s:5:\"xhtml\";s:10:\"field_id_2\";s:936:\"We can repair minor dings and scrapes and carry out general tidy up and refurbishment work aswell as heavy smash repairs which may include replacing entire side panels or complete front or rear end rebuilds which can be carried out using our heavy repair jigs. We also offer a respray service for new vans were they can be painted into what ever colour you wish.\n\nIf your self employed with one van, then we understand the importance of your business, we can assist with your accident claim and get the the vehicle repaired as soon as possible, we may even be able to source a replacement vehicle in 3rd party claims. If you run a larger fleet the we can handle all your accident managent needs, nationwide if need be.\n\nAn end of lease de-fleeting service is also available, if you have a van or vans coming to the end of a contract or lease period then we can take care of de-decaling, cosmetic repairs and valeting to a high standard.\";s:10:\"field_ft_2\";s:5:\"xhtml\";s:10:\"field_id_3\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"field_ft_3\";s:5:\"xhtml\";s:10:\"field_id_4\";s:83:\"<img src=\\\"/siteimages/new-article-01.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Van and LGV accident repairs\\\" />\";s:10:\"field_ft_4\";s:4:\"none\";}'), ('109', '18', '2', '2', '1224911182', 'a:22:{s:9:\"weblog_id\";s:1:\"2\";s:8:\"entry_id\";s:2:\"18\";s:9:\"author_id\";s:1:\"2\";s:10:\"new_weblog\";s:1:\"2\";s:6:\"status\";s:4:\"open\";s:10:\"entry_date\";s:19:\"2006-12-10 03:47 PM\";s:15:\"expiration_date\";s:0:\"\";s:23:\"comment_expiration_date\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"trackback_urls\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"versioning_enabled\";s:1:\"y\";s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"HGV accident repairs\";s:9:\"url_title\";s:3:\"hgv\";s:6:\"submit\";s:6:\"Update\";s:4:\"mode\";s:6:\"normal\";s:10:\"field_id_1\";s:280:\"If your vehicle is damaged in an accident Commercial Colours will look after the repair process from start to finish. We are the only commercial vehicle body shop in the North Wales and North West area fully equipped to deal with even the heaviest of commercial vehicle accidents.\";s:10:\"field_ft_1\";s:5:\"xhtml\";s:10:\"field_id_2\";s:3493:\"<p>After an accident we will arrange collection of your vehicle, even if it is unroadworthy.  It is in your best interest to move any damaged vehicles to Commercial Colours as soon as possible to avoid incurring storage charges whilst the insurance claim in being processed.</p>\n\n<p>Our friendly and efficient administration staff have years of experience in dealing with insurance companies and have built up good working relationships with their engineers. We are approved repairers for Norwich Union and AXA, plus we carry out work for Zurich, Royal and Sun Alliance, Allianz Cornhill, Brit, Ensign, NFU and many of the commercial accident management networks. With just few details from yourselves we can speed up authorisation for repair work to proceed.</p>\n\n<p>For our larger customers we are happy to hold your insurance details on file to allow us to deal with the claim process from start to finish.</p>\n\n<h3>We specialise in the accident repairs to any type of commercial vehicle.</h3>\n\n<p><img src=\\\"../siteimages/article_02b.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"f\\\" />Our fully trained staff have the expertise and years of experience in accident repair work from the smallest to largest of commercial vehicles.  We use the latest methods of repair and are constantly updating our workshop equipment in line with requests from insurance companies and the latest technology.  We also offer continuous training to our staff in repair methods.</p>\n\n<h3>Our fully equipped workshop includes the following items of equipment</h3>\n\n<ul>\n<li>10 Post <a href=\\\"http://www.blackhawk.co.uk/uk/powercage/powercage.html\\\" title=\\\"Black Hawk Powercage\\\">Black Hawk Powercage</a> 250 tonne cold pull jig with Josam lazer measuring system for all multi-axle vehicles for straightening twisted or bent LGV/HGV chassis</li>\n<li><a href=\\\"http://www.josam.se/\\\" title=\\\"Josam \\\">Josam </a>cab repair bench for damaged cab shells.  The bench allows us to realign the floor and cab mounting points, pull pillars upright and renew panels, it often saves on the cost of replacing expensive cab shells.</li>\n<li><a href=\\\"http://www.blackhawk.co.uk/uk/korek/korekfirstpage.html\\\" title=\\\"Korek \\\">Korek </a>floor mounted heavy duty jig systems for vans and 4 x 4â€™s for realigning twisted or impact damaged vehicles. Chassis sections can be reworked into their original positions without the need for replacing complete chassis\\\'.</li>\n<li>Tig, mig, spot and aluminium welding</li>\n<li>Steel sheet and aluminium cutting and fabrication equipment for making replacement panels for buses and coaches</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><img src=\\\"../siteimages/article_06a.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"f\\\" />Together with the experience of our painters, computerised paint matching and mixing scheme and our 18m low bake commercial vehicle spray booth the paint finish on your repaired vehicle will be to pre-accident standard.</p>\n\n<p>On completion of repairs we can arrange our sign writer to make and apply decals to your vehicle, or if you would prefer to use your own sign writer we can liaise with them to ensure your vehicle is ready for the road in its pre-accident condition.</p>\n\n<p><img src=\\\"../siteimages/article_02c.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"f\\\" />On all insurance work the final invoice for the repair will be forwarded direct to your insurance company who will pay us directly (excluding excess or VAT applicable).  This means you do not have to pay for the repairs yourself and wait for your insurance company to reimburse you.</p>\";s:10