iration_date\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"trackback_urls\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"versioning_enabled\";s:1:\"y\";s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"Plant and machinery\";s:9:\"url_title\";s:39:\"plant_and_machinery_repair_and_painting\";s:6:\"submit\";s:6:\"Update\";s:4:\"mode\";s:6:\"normal\";s:10:\"field_id_1\";s:136:\"Commercial Colours offer specialist, professional plant and machinery damage repair and painting services from our workshops in Deeside.\";s:10:\"field_ft_1\";s:5:\"xhtml\";s:10:\"field_id_2\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"field_ft_2\";s:5:\"xhtml\";s:10:\"field_id_3\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"field_ft_3\";s:5:\"xhtml\";s:10:\"field_id_4\";s:53:\"<img src=\\\"../siteimages/article_05.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" />\";s:10:\"field_ft_4\";s:4:\"none\";s:10:\"category_0\";s:1:\"6\";}'), ('96', '32', '2', '2', '1224725374', 'a:22:{s:9:\"weblog_id\";s:1:\"2\";s:8:\"entry_id\";s:2:\"32\";s:9:\"author_id\";s:1:\"2\";s:10:\"new_weblog\";s:1:\"2\";s:6:\"status\";s:4:\"open\";s:10:\"entry_date\";s:19:\"2006-12-15 01:51 PM\";s:15:\"expiration_date\";s:0:\"\";s:23:\"comment_expiration_date\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"trackback_urls\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"versioning_enabled\";s:1:\"y\";s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"New vehicle painting\";s:9:\"url_title\";s:20:\"new_vehicle_painting\";s:6:\"submit\";s:6:\"Update\";s:4:\"mode\";s:6:\"normal\";s:10:\"field_id_1\";s:355:\"We utilise a fully computerised paint mixing scheme provided by <a href=\\\"http://www.glasurit.com/ \\\" title=\\\"Glasurit\\\">Glasurit</a> or <a href=\\\"http://www.sikkenscr.co.uk/sikkens/uk/\\\" title=\\\"Sikkens\\\">Sikkens</a> BTLV system. Both processes are fully EPA compliant and result in a factory finish quality on brand new or resprayed commercial vehicles.\";s:10:\"field_ft_1\";s:5:\"xhtml\";s:10:\"field_id_2\";s:529:\"<p>Prior to painting (truck for example) the vehicle is stripped down to the bare chassis and cab, the chassis is then de-waxed by steam cleaning with detergents. Once dried off the chassis is thoroughly \\\'scotched\\\' from one end to another, the cab, grill, air deflector kit, is abraded with \\\'400\\\' sand paper. Plastic bumpers, wheel arches, skirts and step panels are also \\\'scotched\\\' and prepared with plastic primer. Once masked and cleaned off the Sikkens BTLV 350 process is applied and baked as per their guidlines.</p>\n\";s:10:\"field_ft_2\";s:4:\"none\";s:10:\"field_id_3\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"field_ft_3\";s:5:\"xhtml\";s:10:\"field_id_4\";s:53:\"<img src=\\\"../siteimages/article_04.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" />\";s:10:\"field_ft_4\";s:4:\"none\";}'), ('97', '19', '2', '2', '1224725404', 'a:22:{s:9:\"weblog_id\";s:1:\"2\";s:8:\"entry_id\";s:2:\"19\";s:9:\"author_id\";s:1:\"2\";s:10:\"new_weblog\";s:1:\"2\";s:6:\"status\";s:4:\"open\";s:10:\"entry_date\";s:19:\"2006-12-10 03:50 PM\";s:15:\"expiration_date\";s:0:\"\";s:23:\"comment_expiration_date\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"trackback_urls\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"versioning_enabled\";s:1:\"y\";s:5:\"title\";s:36:\"Refurbishment and paintwork services\";s:9:\"url_title\";s:36:\"refurbishment_and_paintwork_services\";s:6:\"submit\";s:6:\"Update\";s:4:\"mode\";s:6:\"normal\";s:10:\"field_id_1\";s:304:\"Not only do Commercial Colours repair accident damaged vehicles, we also carry out refurbishment work and respraying  to all types of commercial vehicles, including plant and machinery, trailers, tankers, vans, coaches, removal vans, municiple vehicles, horseboxes and any specialist commercial vehicles.\";s:10:\"field_ft_1\";s:5:\"xhtml\";s:10:\"field_id_2\";s:998:\"<p>Whether you are an owner operator or a large company with a fleet of commercial vehicles we have the experience, equipment and contacts with specialist companies to completely refurbish your commercial vehicles. We can carry out shot blasting, panel fabrication and replacement, electrical rewiring and various types of welding.</p>\n\n<p><img src=\\\"../siteimages/article_06b.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"f\\\" /><img src=\\\"../siteimages/article_06c.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"f\\\" />Together with the experience of our painters, computerised paint matching and mixing scheme and our 60\\\' low bake commercial vehicle spray booth the paint finish on your vehicle will be of an exceptionally high standard and guaranteed.</p>\n\n<p>After completion of the refurbishment/respray we will liaise with your sign writers to re-decal the vehicle prior to its return to you, or alternatively we can arrange for our own sign writer to carry out this work. Either way your vehicle is returned to you ready for the road.</p>\";s:10:\"field_ft_2\";s:4:\"none\";s:10:\"field_id_3\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"field_ft_3\";s:5:\"xhtml\";s:10:\"field_id_4\";s:53:\"<img src=\\\"../siteimages/article_03.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" />\";s:10:\"field_ft_4\";s:4:\"none\";}');
