ty of workmanship. More recently, we have used Commercial Colours for our accident repairs and they have dealt with the work in an efficient and professional manner.</p>\n<p>Roland Young Ltd.</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>For the last four years, we have used Commercial Colours to repair all body work damage to our fleet of large goods vehicles and vans. On every occassion, our repaired vehicles have been returned to us in first-class condition. The staff are friendly and helpful and I have no hesitation in recommending Commercial Colours.</p>\n<p>Afonwen Services Ltd.</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>Commercial Colours have looked after our commercial vehicles since 2005. They provide an excellent all-round service and their workmanship is of an exceptionally high standard. </p>\n<p>Flintshire County Council</p>\n</blockquote>\";s:10:\"field_ft_2\";s:4:\"none\";s:10:\"field_id_3\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"field_ft_3\";s:5:\"xhtml\";s:10:\"field_id_4\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"field_ft_4\";s:4:\"none\";s:10:\"category_0\";s:1:\"7\";}'), ('51', '18', '2', '2', '1166233499', 'a:22:{s:9:\"weblog_id\";s:1:\"2\";s:8:\"entry_id\";s:2:\"18\";s:9:\"author_id\";s:1:\"2\";s:10:\"new_weblog\";s:1:\"2\";s:6:\"status\";s:4:\"open\";s:10:\"entry_date\";s:19:\"2006-12-10 03:47 PM\";s:15:\"expiration_date\";s:0:\"\";s:23:\"comment_expiration_date\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"trackback_urls\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"versioning_enabled\";s:1:\"y\";s:5:\"title\";s:33:\"Accident damaged vehicle services\";s:9:\"url_title\";s:33:\"accident_damaged_vehicle_services\";s:6:\"submit\";s:6:\"Update\";s:4:\"mode\";s:6:\"normal\";s:10:\"field_id_1\";s:281:\"If your vehicle is damaged in an accident Commercial Colours will look after the repair process from start to finish. We are the only commercial vehicle body shop in the North Wales and North West areas fully equipped to deal with even the heaviest of commercial vehicle accidents.\";s:10:\"field_ft_1\";s:5:\"xhtml\";s:10:\"field_id_2\";s:2822:\"<p><img src=\\\"../siteimages/article_02.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" /></p>\n\n<p>After an accident we will arrange collection of your vehicle, even if it is unroadworthy.  It is in your best interest to move any damaged vehicles to Commercial Colours as soon as possible to avoid incurring storage charges whilst the insurance claim in being processed.</p>\n<p>Our friendly and efficient administration staff have years of experience in dealing with insurance companies and have built up good working relationships with the insurance engineers.  With a few details from yourselves we can speed up authorisation for repair work to proceed.</p>\n<p>For our larger customers we are happy to hold your insurance details on file to speed up the authorisation process.</p>\n\n<h3>Our fully trained staff have the expertise and years of experience</h3>\n<p><img src=\\\"../siteimages/article_02b.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"f\\\" />Our fully trained staff have the expertise and years of experience in accident/repair work from the smallest to largest of commercial vehicles.  We use the latest methods of repair and are constantly updating our workshop equipment in line with requests from insurance companies and the latest technology.  We also offer continuous training to our staff in repair methods.</p>\n\n<h4>Our fully equipped workshop includes the following items of equipment</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>10 Post Black Hawk Powercage 250 tonne cold pull jig with lazer measuring system for all multi-axle vehicles for straightening twisted or bent LGV/HGV chassis</li>\n<li>Josam cab repair bench for damaged cab shells.  The bench allows us to realign the floor and cab mounting points, pull pillars upright and renew panels</li>\n<li>Korek floor mounted heavy duty jig systems for vans and 4 x 4â€™s for realigning twisted or impact damaged vehicles</li>\n<li>Tig, mig, spot and aluminium welding</li>\n<li>Steel sheet and aluminium cutting and fabrication equipment for making replacement panels for buses and coaches</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><img src=\\\"../siteimages/article_02c.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"f\\\" />Together with the experience of our painters, computerised paint matching and mixing scheme and our 18m low bake commercial vehicle spray booth the paint finish on your vehicle will be of an exceptionally high standard.</p>\n<p>On completion of repairs we can arrange our sign writer to make and apply decals to your vehicle, or if you would prefer to use your own sign writer we can liase with them to ensure your vehicle is ready for the road in its pre-accident condition.</p>\n<p>On all insurance work the final invoice for the repair will be forwarded direct to your insurance company who will pay us directly (excluding excess or VAT applicable).  This means you do not have to pay for the repairs yourself and wait for your insurance company to reimburse you.</p>\";s:10:\"field_ft_2\";s:4:\"none\";s:10:\"field_id_3\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"field_ft_3\";s:5:\"xhtml\";s:10:\"field_id_4\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"field_ft_4\";s:4:\"none\";}'), ('52', '19', '2', '2', '1166233609', 'a:22:{s:9:\"weblog_id\";s:1:\"2\";s:8:\"entry_id\";s:2:\"19\";s:9:\"author_id\";s:1:\"2\";s:10:\"new_weblog\";s:1:\"2\";s:6:\"status\";s:4:\"open\";s:10:\"entry_date\";s:19:\"2006-12-10 03:50 PM\";s:15:\"expiration_date\";s:0:\"\";s:23:\"comment_expiration_date\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"trackback_urls\";s:0:\"\";s:18:\"versioning_enabled\";s:1:\"y\";s:5:\"title\";s:36:\"Refurbishment and paintwork services\";s:9:\"url_title\";s:36:\"refurbishment_and_paintwork_services\";s:6:\"submit\";s:6:\"Update\";s:4:\"mode\";s:6:\"normal\";s:10:\"field_id_1\";s:252:\"Not only do Commercial Colours repair accident damaged vehicles, we also carry out refurbishment work on all types of commercial vehicle, including plant and machinery, trailers, tankers, vans, coaches, horseboxes and any specialist commercial vehicle.\";s:10:\"field_ft_1\";s:5:\"xhtml\";s:10:\"field_id_2\";s:1059:\"<p><img src=\\\"../siteimages/article_03.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" /></p