 shells.  The bench allows us to realign the floor and cab mounting points, pull pillars upright and renew panels, it often saves on the cost of replacing expensive cab shells.</li>\n<li><a href=\\\"http://www.blackhawk.co.uk/uk/korek/korekfirstpage.html\\\" title=\\\"Korek \\\">Korek </a>floor mounted heavy duty jig systems for vans and 4 x 4â€™s for realigning twisted or impact damaged vehicles. Chassis sections can be reworked into their original positions without the need for replacing complete chassis\\\'.</li>\n<li>Tig, mig, spot and aluminium welding</li>\n<li>Steel sheet and aluminium cutting and fabrication equipment for making replacement panels for buses and coaches</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><img src=\\\"../siteimages/article_06a.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"f\\\" />Together with the experience of our painters, computerised paint matching and mixing scheme and our 18m low bake commercial vehicle spray booth the paint finish on your repaired vehicle will be to pre-accident standard.</p>\n<p>On completion of repairs we can arrange our sign writer to make and apply decals to your vehicle, or if you would prefer to use your own sign writer we can liaise with them to ensure your vehicle is ready for the road in its pre-accident condition.</p>\n<p><img src=\\\"../siteimages/article_02c.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"f\\\" />On all insurance work the final invoice for the repair will be forwarded direct to your insurance company who will pay us directly (excluding excess or VAT applicable).  This means you do not have to pay for the repairs yourself and wait for your insurance company to reimburse you.</p>\";s:10:\"field_ft_2\";s:4:\"none\";s:10:\"field_id_3\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"field_ft_3\";s:5:\"xhtml\";s:10:\"field_id_4\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"field_ft_4\";s:4:\"none\";}'), ('92', '19', '2', '2', '1212172572', 'a:22:{s:9:\"weblog_id\";s:1:\"2\";s:8:\"entry_id\";s:2:\"19\";s:9:\"author_id\";s:1:\"2\";s:10:\"new_weblog\";s:1:\"2\";s:6:\"status\";s:4:\"open\";s:10:\"entry_date