ent and repairs, Korek light commercial repair jigs, commercial vehicle spray booths and shot blasting. </p>\n\n<h4>Manufacturer approved repairs</h4>\n\n<p>We are leading CV crash repair specialists and approved repairers for <a href=\"http://www2.mercedes-benz.co.uk/\">Mercedes Benz UK</a> and <a href=\"http://www.scania.co.uk/ \">Scania Great Britain</a>. Our staff also have extensive experience with <a href=\"http://www.daftrucks.co.uk/\">DAF</a>, <a href=\"http://www.volvo.co.uk/\">Volvo</a>, <a href=\"http://www.man.co.uk/\">MAN</a> and <a href=\"http://www.iveco.co.uk/\">Iveco</a>, as well as <a href=\"http://www.ford.co.uk/\">Ford</a>, <a href=\"http://www.renault.co.uk/\">Renault</a> and <a href=\"http://www.vauxhall.co.uk/\">Vauxhall</a>.</p>\n\n<h4>Insurance approved</h4>\n\n<p>We handle the repair process from start to finish. We are approved commercial vehicle repairers for Norwich Union, AXA, Royal &amp; Sun Alliance and Quinn Direct. LCV\'s and van accident repairs are catered for with an accident management service for larger fleets.</p>\n\n<h4>Defleeting and end of contract service</h4>\n\n<p>End of contract and defleeting services are available from de-decaling and valeting through to complete refurbishments. We offer a nationwide collection service and secure storage.</p>\n</div>', '', '1370614334', '0', 'n', '0', '', 'n', 'n', 'o', '0'), ('41', '1', '4', 'content_supp', 'n', 'webpage', '<div>\n{exp:weblog:entries weblog=\"company\" limit=\"1\" dynamic=\"off\" category=\"5\"}\n<h3><a href=\"{title_permalink=\"company/index\"}\">{title}</a></h3>\n{summary}\n{/exp:weblog:entries}\n</div>\n\n<div>\n{exp:weblog:entries weblog=\"company\" limit=\"1\" dynamic=\"off\" category=\"6\"}\n<h3><a href=\"{title_permalink=\"company/index\"}\">{title}</a></h3>\n{summary}\n{/exp:weblog:entries}\n</div>\n\n<div>\n{exp:weblog:entries weblog=\"company\" limit=\"1\" dynamic=\"off\" category=\"7\"}\n<h3><a href=\"{title_permalink=\"company/index\"}\">{title}</a></h3>\