INSERT INTO `exp_weblog_data` VALUES ('3', '1', '2', 'Commercial Colours became an independent company and relocated to new premises on Deeside Industrial Park in August 2005. All of the equipment and staff from the operation in Llandudno was transferred to the new premises to allow us to continue offering the wide range of high quality commercial vehicle accident repair and painting services our customers had become accustomed to.', 'xhtml', '<h3>We now employ over twenty staff</h3>\n<p>Over the last 12 months we have continued to increase in size and now employ over twenty staff with the experience and knowledge of the industry to ensure a speedy repair with a top quality finish.</p>\n<p>We also employ apprentices, who, with the assistance of our local colleges, we hope to have as fully qualified bodywork technicians within due course.  We feel that it is of great importance to provide young people with the qualifications and experience in the trade for the future of the industry.</p>', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '<img src=\"../siteimages/new-article-05.jpg\" alt=\"\" />', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'none', '', 'xhtml'), ('34', '1', '2', 'Commercial Colours cater for the lighter side of accident repairs, from car derived vans such as Astra vans, Berlingos, Partners, Connects right up to Ford Transits, VW Crafters and Mercedes Sprinters, even the long wheel base high roof versions. ', 'xhtml', '<p>We can repair minor dings and scrapes and carry out general tidy up and refurbishment work as well as heavy smash repairs which may include replacing entire side panels or complete front or rear end rebuilds which can be carried out using our heavy repair jigs. We also offer a respray service for new vans where they can be painted into what ever colour you wish.</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"../siteimages/article_07a.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"f\" />If your self employed with one van, then we understand the importance of your business, we can assist with your accident claim and get the the vehicle repaired as soon as possible, we may even be able to source a replacement vehicle in 3rd party claims. If you run a larger fleet the we can handle all your accident managent needs, nationwide if need be.</p>\n\n<p>An end of lease de-fleeting service is also available, if you have a van or vans coming to the end of a contract or lease period then we can take care of de-decaling, cosmetic repairs and valeting to a high standard.</p>', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '<img src=\"/siteimages/new-article-01.jpg\" alt=\"Van and LGV accident repairs\" />', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml'), ('4', '1', '2', 'If you would like more information about our services, please complete the form below. <a href=\"{path=\"company/index\"}privacy_policy\">Privacy policy</a>  We hate SPAM too. Alternatively, please call in to see us at <a href=\"http://maps.google.co.uk/maps?f=q&amp;hl=en&amp;q=CH5+2LL&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;om=1&amp;z=16&amp;iwloc=addr\" title=\"Find us on Google Maps\">our workshops</a>', 'xhtml', '', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'none', '', 'xhtml'), ('29', '1', '2', 'Yes. We courtesy vehicle fleet includes two tractor units, one Vito and one Sprinter van, plus two Vauxhall Combi vans.', 'xhtml', 'If you are involved in a non-fault accident, we can forward your details to <a href=\"http://www.bvh.co.uk/recovery.htm\">RTA Recovery Services</a> who will assess your situation and provide you with a vehicle, free of charge, if you qualify and subject to availability. They will invoice the other party\'s insurance direct, meaning you avoid any financial outlay.', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml'), ('28', '1', '2', 'Providing you have informed your insurance company of your claim Commercial Colours can contact them to speed up the process of having the repairs carried out. We have an excellent working relationship with many insurance companies and their engineers which simplifies the often complicated claim process.', 'xhtml', 'Simply contact us with your insurance company name and your policy number and we will do the rest.', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml'), ('26', '1', '2', '<p>This will depend on the extent of the damage, condition of the vehicle and the finish required. Please complete our <a href=\"/index.php/company/quote\">estimate request form</a> for a no obligation quotation and please attach photographs wherever possible.</p>', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml'), ('24', '1', '2', 'Commercial Colours Ltd have been growing steadily since our relocation in August 2005. We plan to expand during years to come and would welcome a good database of potential employees.', 'xhtml', '<p>If you are looking for work in the Bodyshop trade and have experience in working with commercial vehicles please forward your CV to Mark Jacques at:</p>\n\n<div class=\"vcard\">\n<div class=\"fn org\">Commercial Colours</div>\n<div class=\"adr\">\n<div class=\"street-address\">Zone 3, Link 56, Weighbridge Road</div>\n<div>Deeside Industrial Park</div>\n<div class=\"locality\">Deeside</div>\n<div class=\"region\">Flintshire</div>\n<div class=\"postal-code\">CH5 2LL</div>\n</div >\n<div class=\"tel\">Phone: 01244 281352</div>\n</div >', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml'), ('25', '1', '2', '', 'xhtml', '<p>This privacy statement covers the Commercial Colours web site.</p>\n\n<h3>Information collection</h3>\n<p>Commercial Colours Ltd. is the sole owner of the information collected on this web site. We collect information from our visitors at several different points on our web site.</p>\n\n<h3>News-letter registration</h3>\n<p>In order to receive our news-letters, visitors must first complete the registration form. During registration visitors give their email address. This information is used to deliver the news-letter.</p>\n\n<h3>Cookies</h3>\n<p>A cookie is a piece of data stored on the visitor\'s computer tied to information about the visitor. Cookies are not linked to any personally identifiable information. Cookies can be removed by following browser help files.</p>\n\n<h3>Log files</h3>\n<p>Like most standard Web site servers we use log files. This includes internet protocol (IP) addresses, browser type, internet service provider (ISP), referring/exit pages, platform type, date/time stamp, and number of clicks to analyse trends. IP addresses, etc. are not linked to any personally identifiable information.</p>\n\n<h3>Legal disclaimer</h3>\n<p>We may need to disclose personal information where it is necessary to comply with a current judicial proceeding, a court order or legal process served on our web site.</p>\n\n<h3>Links</h3>\n<p>Our web site contains links to other sites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these other sites. This privacy statement applies solely to information collected by our web site.</p>', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml'), ('18', '1', '2', 'If your vehicle is damaged in an accident Commercial Colours will look after the repair process from start to finish. We are the only commercial vehicle body shop in the North Wales and North West area fully equipped to deal with even the heaviest of commercial vehicle accidents.', 'xhtml', '<p>After an accident we will arrange collection of your vehicle, even if it is unroadworthy.  It is in your best interest to move any damaged vehicles to Commercial Colours as soon as possible to avoid incurring storage charges whilst the insurance claim in being processed.</p>\n\n<p>Our friendly and efficient administration staff have years of experience in dealing with insurance companies and have built up good working relationships with their engineers. Norwich Union, AXA, Royal &amp; Sun Alliance and Quinn Direct, plus we carry out work for Zurich, Allianz Cornhill, Brit, Ensign, NFU and many of the commercial accident management networks. With just few details from yourselves we can speed up authorisation for repair work to proceed.</p>\n\n<p>For our larger customers we are happy to hold your insurance details on file to allow us to deal with the claim process from start to finish.</p>\n\n<h3>We specialise in the accident repairs to any type of commercial vehicle.</h3>\n\n<p><img src=\"../siteimages/article_02b.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"f\" />Our fully trained staff have the expertise and years of experience in accident repair work from the smallest to largest of commercial vehicles.  We use the latest methods of repair and are constantly updating our workshop equipment in line with requests from insurance companies and the latest technology.  We also offer continuous training to our staff in repair methods.</p>\n\n<h3>Our fully equipped workshop includes the following items of equipment</h3>\n\n<ul>\n<li>40\' Josam chassis frame alignment system and heat inductor with lazer measuring for multi-axle vehicles for straightening twisted or bent LGV/HGV chassis.</li>\n\n<li><a href=\"http://www.josam.se/\">Josam </a>cab repair bench for damaged cab shells.  The bench allows us to realign the floor and cab mounting points, pull pillars upright and renew panels, it often saves on the cost of replacing expensive cab shells.</li>\n\n<li><a href=\"http://www.blackhawk.co.uk/uk/korek/korekfirstpage.html\" title=\"Korek \">Korek </a>floor mounted heavy duty jig systems for vans and 4 x 4â€™s for realigning twisted or impact damaged vehicles. Chassis sections can be reworked into their original positions without the need for replacing complete chassis\'.</li>\n\n<li>Tig, mig, spot and aluminium welding</li>\n\n<li>Steel sheet and aluminium cutting and fabrication equipment for making replacement panels for buses and coaches</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><img src=\"../siteimages/article_06a.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"f\" />Together with the experience of our painters, computerised paint matching and mixing scheme and our 18m low bake commercial vehicle spray booth the paint finish on your repaired vehicle will be to pre-accident standard.</p>\n\n<p>On completion of repairs we can arrange our sign writer to make and apply decals to your vehicle, or if you would prefer to use your own sign writer we can liaise with them.</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"../siteimages/article_02c.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"f\" />On all insurance work the final invoice for the repair will be forwarded direct to your insurance company who will pay us directly (excluding excess or VAT applicable).  This means you do not have to pay for the repairs yourself and wait for your insurance company to reimburse you.</p>', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '<img src=\"/siteimages/new-article-06.jpg\" alt=\"HGV accident repairs\" />', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml'), ('8', '1', '2', '', 'xhtml', '<blockquote>\n<p>Commercial Colours have provided Great Bear Distribution with all aspects of commercial vehicle repairs for the past ten years. These have included small panels to full cab repairs and have all been to the highest of standards. We have found that Commercial Colours not only provide excellent quality but also provide excellent service and support which includes replacement courtesy vehicles. As a valued customer I would have no hesitation in recommending their services to anyone and they will be our first point of contact for all our commercial vehicle accident repairs.</p>\n<p>Ricky Hughes - Great Bear Distribution</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>Our dealings with Commercial Colours have ranged from complete rebuilding of an HGV to run-of-the-mill standard paint jobs for new tractor units and rigids. We have found all of their work to be of the highest quality and craftsmanship. I have no hesitation in recommending Commercial Colours for any major rebuilding or preparation.</p>\n<p>Allan Morris Transport</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>Commercial Colours have been painting our tractor units, trailers and eight-wheelers for many years and we have always been delighted with the quality of workmanship. More recently, we have used Commercial Colours for our accident repairs and they have dealt with the work in an efficient and professional manner.</p>\n<p>Roland Young Ltd.</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>For the last four years, we have used Commercial Colours to repair all body work damage to our fleet of large goods vehicles and vans. On every occassion, our repaired vehicles have been returned to us in first-class condition. The staff are friendly and helpful and I have no hesitation in recommending Commercial Colours.</p>\n<p>Afonwen Services Ltd.</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>Commercial Colours have looked after our commercial vehicles since 2005. They provide an excellent all-round service and their workmanship is of an exceptionally high standard. </p>\n<p>Flintshire County Council</p>\n</blockquote>', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'none', '', 'xhtml'), ('19', '1', '2', 'Not only do Commercial Colours repair accident damaged vehicles, we also carry out refurbishment work and respraying  to all types of commercial vehicles, including plant and machinery, trailers, tankers, vans, coaches, removal vans, municiple vehicles, horseboxes and any specialist commercial vehicles.', 'xhtml', '<p>Whether you are an owner operator or a large company with a fleet of commercial vehicles we have the experience, equipment and contacts with specialist companies to completely refurbish your commercial vehicles. We can carry out shot blasting, panel fabrication and replacement, electrical rewiring and various types of welding.</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"../siteimages/article_06b.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"f\" /><img src=\"../siteimages/article_06c.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"f\" />Together with the experience of our painters, computerised paint matching and mixing scheme and our 60\' low bake commercial vehicle spray booth the paint finish on your vehicle will be of an exceptionally high standard and guaranteed.</p>\n\n<p>After completion of the refurbishment/respray we will liaise with your sign writers to re-decal the vehicle prior to its return to you, or alternatively we can arrange for our own sign writer to carry out this work. Either way your vehicle is returned to you ready for the road.</p>', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml'), ('30', '1', '2', 'Yes, Commercial Colours were recently awarded VBRA membership, which also incorporates an Office of Fair Trading Approved Code.', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml'), ('31', '1', '2', 'Yes, any parts replaced are covered by the manufacturers\' warranty, plus any repairs and paint work we carry out is guaranteed.', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml'), ('32', '1', '2', 'We utilise fully computerised paint mixing schemes provided by <a href=\"http://www.glasurit.com/ \">Glasurit</a> or <a href=\"http://www.ppg.com\">PPG</a>. Both processes are fully EPA compliant and result in a factory finish quality on brand new or resprayed commercial vehicles.', 'xhtml', '<p>Prior to painting (truck for example) the vehicle is stripped down to the bare chassis and cab, the chassis is then de-waxed by steam cleaning with detergents. Once dried off the chassis is thoroughly \'scotched\' from one end to another, the cab, grille, air deflector kit, is abraded with \'400\' sand paper. Plastic bumpers, wheel arches, skirts and step panels are also \'scotched\' and prepared with plastic primer. Once masked and cleaned off the chosen process is applied and baked in one of our three spray booths.</p>\n', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '<img src=\"../siteimages/new-article-02.jpg\" alt=\"New vehicle painting\" />', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml'), ('33', '1', '2', 'Commercial Colours offer specialist, professional plant and machinery damage repair and painting services from our workshops in Deeside.', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '<img src=\"../siteimages/new-article-07.jpg\" alt=\"Plant and machinery\" />', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml'), ('35', '1', '2', 'Yes. All of our painting processes are carried out following strict environmental guidelines. We are EPA registered with the local authority and we use fully compliant products including water-based paints. Waste paint and thinners are recycled and re-used onsite.', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml');
